---
const downloadPath = '/downloads/codex-pet-alpha-v1.0.zip';
const thumbnailPath = '/images/alphabeta/codex-pet/alpha-share.png';
const packageSize = '1.9MB';
---

<section class="py-20 bg-brand-beige border-y border-brand-pink/10">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-8 max-w-6xl">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-brand-pink/20 bg-white shadow-sm">
        <img
          src={thumbnailPath}
          alt="Codex Petとして配布しているαのサムネイル"
          class="aspect-[1200/630] w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          width="1200"
          height="630"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-7">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.32em] uppercase text-brand-pink-accent/80">
            Codex Pet
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-bold leading-snug text-gray-900">
            αを、Codexの小さな相棒として配布しています。
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-7 text-brand-gray/70">
            αβlabのキャラクター「α」をCodex Pet用のZIPにしました。中身はpet.json、spritesheet.webp、README、利用条件、チェックサムのみで、API情報や個人情報は含まれていません。
          </p>
          <ol class="space-y-2 text-sm leading-6 text-brand-gray/70">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="font-bold text-brand-pink-accent">1.</span>
              <span>ZIPを解凍します。</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="font-bold text-brand-pink-accent">2.</span>
              <span>解凍した<code class="mx-1 rounded bg-white/70 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[0.9em]">alpha</code>フォルダを<code class="mx-1 rounded bg-white/70 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[0.9em]">~/.codex/pets/</code>に入れて、Codexを起動します。表示されない場合は、Codexのアバター/Pet設定から<code class="mx-1 rounded bg-white/70 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[0.9em]">alpha</code>を選択してください。</span>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {['offline zip', 'codex pet', 'non-commercial', 'alpha'].map(tag => (
            <span class="rounded-full border border-brand-pink/25 bg-white/70 px-4 py-2 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-gray/60">
              {tag}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href={downloadPath}
            download
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-2xl bg-brand-gray px-8 py-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-beige transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            Download ZIP
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-1m-4-4-4 4m0 0-4-4m4 4V4"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/alphabeta/guidelines/"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-brand-pink/30 bg-white/70 px-8 py-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-pink-accent transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-lg"
          >
            Usage Guidelines
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-brand-gray/45">
          codex-pet-alpha-v1.0.zip / {packageSize}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
